    PdfWorker -->|"reads input, writes result"| MinIO
    TabularWorker -->|"reads input, writes result"| MinIO
    PdfWorker -->|"same chat contract"| ProviderRouter
    TabularWorker -->|"same chat contract"| ProviderRouter

    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|"scrapes /metrics"| Backend
    Prometheus -->|"scrapes /metrics"| VLLM
